                                          'the process. Patience and '
                                          'respectful follow-ups (after a '
                                          'reasonable interval) are '
                                          'appreciated.</p>\n'
                                          '<h3 id="s-on-ai-usage">On AI '
                                          'Usage</h3>\n'
                                          '<p>We recognize that AI tools are '
                                          'now part of many developers’ '
                                          'workflows. Using AI to explore '
                                          'documentation, clarify syntax, or '
                                          'organize thoughts is not inherently '
                                          'a problem.</p>\n'
                                          '<p>However, AI must not replace '
