                                          'decisions, justify trade-offs, and '
                                          'respond thoughtfully when '
                                          'challenged. If you cannot defend '
                                          'your own proposal without external '
                                          'assistance, it signals a lack of '
                                          'readiness for this kind of '
                                          'work.</p>\n'
                                          '<p>The quality we look for is not '
                                          'perfect language — it is depth of '
                                          'understanding.</p>\n'
                                          '<h3 '
                                          'id="s-im-a-first-time-contributor-to-django-what-should-i-do">I’m '
                                          'a First-Time Contributor to Django '
                                          '— What Should I Do?</h3>\n'
                                          '<p>If this is your first time '
