                                          'conference?</h4>\n'
                                          '<p>I think our industry (and even '
                                          'the world in general) is in a very '
                                          'different place today than a decade '
                                          'ago when I was actively organizing '
                                          "conferences. Honestly I'm not sure "
                                          'it would be as easy today to do the '
                                          "things we've done.</p>\n"
                                          '<p>My recommendation is to do it if '
