                                          'Ecosystem</a> page \n'
                                          'which highlights several amazing '
                                          'resources to keep in touch with '
                                          'what is going on with Django, how '
                                          'to find \n'
                                          'recommended packages, and a sample '
                                          'list of those packages the Steering '
