                                          'control characters</h4>\n'
                                          '<ul class="simple">\n'
                                          '<li>On the <a class="reference '
                                          'external" '
                                          'href="https://github.com/django/django/commit/e891a84c7ef9962bfcc3b4685690219542f86a22">main '
                                          'branch</a></li>\n'
                                          '<li>On the <a class="reference '
