e adopted the pass. The new rate applies to eligible vehicles at approximately 1,150 fee plazas.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'The National Highways Authority of India is increasing the FASTag Annual Pass fee. Starting April 1, 2026, the pass will cost Rs 3,075. This prepaid toll plan is for non-commercial private vehicles. The revision aligns with National Highways Fee Rules. Over 56 lakh users have adopted the pass. The new rate applies to eligible vehicles at approximately 1,150 fee plazas.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/technology/tech-news/nhai-increases-fastag-annual-pass-fee-starting-april-1-2026-users-to-pay-/articleshow/129587445.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '27818', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129587440,imgsize-27818.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/technology/tech-news/nhai-increases-fastag-annual-pass-fee-starting-april-1-2026-users-to-pay-/articleshow/129587445.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/technology/tech-news/nhai-increases-fastag-annual-pass-fee-starting-april-1-2026-users-to-pay-/articleshow/129587445.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Sun, 15 Mar 2026 14:57:19 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=15, tm_hour=9, tm_min=27, tm_sec=19, tm_wday=6, tm_yday=74, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI TECH DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI TECH DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI TECH DESK'}}, {'title': 'Happy Chaitra Navratri 2026: Top 50 wishes, messages and quotes for loved ones', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Happy Chaitra Navratri 2026: Top 50 wishes, messages and quotes for loved ones'}, 'summary': 'Chaitra Navratri, a significant Hindu festival marking the lunar New Year, commences in 2026, dedicated to Goddess Durga and her nine forms. Devotees observe fasts, offer prayers, and seek blessings for prosperity and happiness. The nine-day celebration symbolizes the triumph of good over evil, fostering faith and positivity. Families and friends exchange heartfelt wishes, strengthening bonds during this auspicious period.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Chaitra Navratri, a significant Hindu festival marking the lunar New Year, commences in 2026, dedicated to Goddess Durga and her nine forms. Devotees observe fasts, offer prayers, and seek blessings for prosperity and happiness. The nine-day celebration symbolizes the triumph of good over evil, fostering faith and positivity. Families and friends exchange heartfelt wishes, strengthening bonds during this auspicious period.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/events/happy-chaitra-navratri-2026-top-50-wishes-messages-greetings-quotes-images-whatsapp-and-facebook-status-to-share-with-your-loved-ones/articleshow/129608027.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '1975915', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129608130,imgsize-1975915.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/events/happy-chaitra-navratri-2026-top-50-wishes-messages-greetings-quotes-images-whatsapp-and-facebook-status-to-share-with-your-loved-ones/articleshow/129608027.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/events/happy-chaitra-navratri-2026-top-50-wishes-messages-greetings-quotes-images-whatsapp-and-facebook-status-to-share-with-your-loved-ones/articleshow/129608027.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 20:48:00 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=15, tm_min=18, tm_sec=0, tm_wd