 with one new mock draft projecting Indiana QB Fernando Mendoza to the Raiders, the message feels loud, expensive, and impossible to miss.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/nfl/news/nfl-free-agency-maxx-crosby-co-poach-28m-center-from-ravens-in-massive-reset-of-the-entire-position-market/articleshow/129612735.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '118776', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129612769,imgsize-118776.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/nfl/news/nfl-free-agency-maxx-crosby-co-poach-28m-center-from-ravens-in-massive-reset-of-the-entire-position-market/articleshow/129612735.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/nfl/news/nfl-free-agency-maxx-crosby-co-poach-28m-center-from-ravens-in-massive-reset-of-the-entire-position-market/articleshow/129612735.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 20:19:13 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=14, tm_min=49, tm_sec=13, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'NATASHA BOSE'}], 'author': 'NATASHA BOSE', 'author_detail': {'name': 'NATASHA BOSE'}}, {'title': 'UK will not be drawn into ‘wider war’ in Middle East, says PM Keir Starmer', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'UK will not be drawn into ‘wider war’ in Middle East, says PM Keir Starmer'}, 'summary': 'Britain will not join a wider Middle East war, Prime Minister Keir Starmer stated, despite collaborating with allies on a plan to reopen the Strait of Hormuz.  He emphasized restoring shipping flows and global market stability, ruling out a NATO mission.  Starmer stressed the need for a collective, viable plan, not a direct military conflict.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Britain will not join a wider Middle East war, Prime Minister Keir Starmer stated, despite collaborating with allies on a plan to reopen the Strait of Hormuz.  He emphasized restoring shipping flows and global market stability, ruling out a NATO mission.  Starmer stressed the need for a collective, viable plan, not a direct military conflict.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-will-not-be-drawn-into-wider-war-in-middle-east-says-pm-keir-starmer-seeks-allied-plan-to-reopen-strait-of-hormuz/articleshow/129611995.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '66172', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129612248,imgsize-66172.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-will-not-be-drawn-into-wider-war-in-middle-east-says-pm-keir-starmer-seeks-allied-plan-to-reopen-strait-of-hormuz/articleshow/129611995.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-will-not-be-drawn-into-wider-war-in-middle-east-says-pm-keir-starmer-seeks-allied-plan-to-reopen-strait-of-hormuz/articleshow/129611995.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 19:50:47 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=14, tm_min=20, tm_sec=47, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI WORLD DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI WORLD DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI WORLD DESK'}}, {'title': 'Divyanka Tripathi and Vivek Dahiya expecting their first child - Exclusive', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Divyanka Tripathi and Vivek Dahiya expecting their first child - Exclusive'}, 'summary': 'Divyanka Tripathi and Vivek Dahiya are set to welcome their first child, bringing immense joy to their families. The couple, who met on the sets of Yeh Hai Mohabbatein, are also 