ragpur Sadar. These announcements precede the two-phase elections scheduled for April 23 and 29, with vote counting on May 4.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'The BJP has unveiled its initial candidate list for 144 West Bengal assembly seats, featuring prominent figures like Suvendu Adhikari, who will contest from Bhabanipur and Nandigram, challenging Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee. Dilip Ghosh is set to run from Kharagpur Sadar. These announcements precede the two-phase elections scheduled for April 23 and 29, with vote counting on May 4.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/west-bengal-polls-2026-bjp-releases-candidates-for-144-seats-in-1st-list-fields-suvendu-adhikari-in-mamatas-bhabanipur/articleshow/129608686.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '47354', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129608865,imgsize-47354.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/west-bengal-polls-2026-bjp-releases-candidates-for-144-seats-in-1st-list-fields-suvendu-adhikari-in-mamatas-bhabanipur/articleshow/129608686.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/west-bengal-polls-2026-bjp-releases-candidates-for-144-seats-in-1st-list-fields-suvendu-adhikari-in-mamatas-bhabanipur/articleshow/129608686.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 17:05:12 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=11, tm_min=35, tm_sec=12, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI NEWS DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}}, {'title': "'When they are shot, I will be at peace': Delhi Uttam Nagar murder victim's mother demands justice", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "'When they are shot, I will be at peace': Delhi Uttam Nagar murder victim's mother demands justice"}, 'summary': "A 26-year-old man was killed in Delhi's Uttam Nagar after a Holi celebration dispute over a water balloon escalated into violence. His mother demands strict action, alleging the accused threatened her granddaughter and assaulted her family. The family seeks severe punishment for the perpetrators.", 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "A 26-year-old man was killed in Delhi's Uttam Nagar after a Holi celebration dispute over a water balloon escalated into violence. His mother demands strict action, alleging the accused threatened her granddaughter and assaulted her family. The family seeks severe punishment for the perpetrators."}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/when-they-are-shot-i-will-be-at-peace-uttam-nagar-murder-victims-mother-demands-justice/articleshow/129602262.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '64324', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129602332,imgsize-64324.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/when-they-are-shot-i-will-be-at-peace-uttam-nagar-murder-victims-mother-demands-justice/articleshow/129602262.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/delhi/when-they-are-shot-i-will-be-at-peace-uttam-nagar-murder-victims-mother-demands-justice/articleshow/129602262.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:11:49 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=6, tm_min=41, tm_sec=49, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TNN'}], 'author': 'TNN', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TNN'}}, {'title': 'Rasgulla stuck in throat: Man chokes to death at wedding feast', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Rasgulla stuck in throat: Man chokes to death at wedding feast'}, 'summary': 'A tragic incident unfolded at a wedding feast in Jamshedpur, Jharkhand, where a 41-year-old man, Lalit Singh, succumbed to death. A rasgulla reportedly became lodged in his throat, completely blocking his airway and cutting off oxygen supply. He collapsed during the meal and tragically passed away within minutes despite immediate efforts to seek medical assistance.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'A tragic incident unfolded at a wedding feast in Jamshedpur, Jharkhand, where a 41-year-old man, Lalit Singh, succumbed to death. A rasgulla reportedly became lodged in his throat, completely blocking his airway and cutting off oxygen supply. He collapsed during the meal and tragically passed away within minutes despite immediate efforts to seek medical assistance.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/jamshedpur/rasgulla-stuck-in-throat-man-chokes-to-death-at-wedding-feast/articleshow/129602629.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '11852', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129602769,imgsize-11852.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/jamshedpur/rasgulla-stuck-in-throat-man-chokes-to-death-at-wedding-feast/articleshow/129602629.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/jamshedpur/rasgulla-stuck-in-throat-man-chokes-to-death-at-wedding-feast/articleshow/129602629.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 12:31:25 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=7, tm_min=1, tm_sec=25, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TNN'}], 'author': 'TNN', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TNN'}}, {'title': "Kyle Daukaus says he doesn't deserve UFC White House card, talks Bo Nickal fight", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Kyle Daukaus says he doesn't deserve UFC White House card, talks Bo Nickal fight"}, 'summary': '\u200bUnranked middleweight fighter Kyle Daukaus has openly admitted that he understands the criticism surrounding his place in the historic UFC event scheduled at the White House. The fighter is set to face rising prospect Bo Nickal on the undercard of a blockbuster show planned to celebrate the 80th birthday of Donald Trump. The event is expected to take place on the South Lawn and mark the 250th anniversary celebration of the United States.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': '\u200bUnranked middleweight fighter Kyle Daukaus has openly admitted that he understands the criticism surrounding his place in the historic UFC event scheduled at the White House. The fighter is set to face rising prospect Bo Nickal on the undercard of a blockbuster show planned to celebrate the 80th birthday of Donald Trump. The event is expected to take place on the South Lawn and mark the 250th anniversary celebration of the United States.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/mma/news/kyle-daukaus-reveals-why-he-feels-he-doesnt-deserve-a-spot-at-the-ufc-white-house-card-middleweight-fighter-opens-up-on-his-bout-with-bo-nickal/articleshow/129611594.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '843384', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129611581,imgsize-843384.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/mma/news/kyle-daukaus-reveals-why-he-feels-he-doesnt-deserve-a-spot-at-the-ufc-white-house-card-middleweight-fighter-opens-up-on-his-bout-with-bo-nickal/articleshow/129611594.cms', 