ernight in Beed district. Police arrested her 29-year-old former boyfriend based on her statement. The incident highlights a disturbing act of violence and the subsequent legal proceedings initiated by the authorities.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'A 17-year-old girl was allegedly kidnapped, raped, and tied to a pole overnight in Beed district. Police arrested her 29-year-old former boyfriend based on her statement. The incident highlights a disturbing act of violence and the subsequent legal proceedings initiated by the authorities.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/aurangabad/maharashtra-shocker-ex-boyfriend-rapes-ties-minor-girl-to-pole-overnight-in-beed-arrested/articleshow/129605172.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '412884', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129605226,imgsize-412884.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/aurangabad/maharashtra-shocker-ex-boyfriend-rapes-ties-minor-girl-to-pole-overnight-in-beed-arrested/articleshow/129605172.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/aurangabad/maharashtra-shocker-ex-boyfriend-rapes-ties-minor-girl-to-pole-overnight-in-beed-arrested/articleshow/129605172.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 14:37:32 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=9, tm_min=7, tm_sec=32, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'PRASAD JOSHI'}], 'author': 'PRASAD JOSHI', 'author_detail': {'name': 'PRASAD JOSHI'}}, {'title': "Kerala polls: BJP's 1st list of 47 candidates out; fields Rajeev Chandrasekhar, K Surendran", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Kerala polls: BJP's 1st list of 47 candidates out; fields Rajeev Chandrasekhar, K Surendran"}, 'summary': 'The Bharatiya Janata Party has announced its initial list of 47 candidates for the upcoming Kerala assembly elections. Key leaders like Rajeev Chandrasekhar and K Surendran are among those fielded. The party aims to contest across various constituencies in the state. Kerala will go to polls on April 9, with results declared on May 4.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'The Bharatiya Janata Party has announced its initial list of 47 candidates for the upcoming Kerala assembly elections. Key leaders like Rajeev Chandrasekhar and K Surendran are among those fielded. The party aims to contest across various constituencies in the state. Kerala will go to polls on April 9, with results declared on May 4.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/kerala-elections-2026-bjp-releases-first-list-of-47-candidates-fields-rajeev-chandrasekhar-k-surendran/articleshow/129608012.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '1003192', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129608145,imgsize-1003192.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/kerala-elections-2026-bjp-releases-first-list-of-47-candidates-fields-rajeev-chandrasekhar-k-surendran/articleshow/129608012.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/kerala-elections-2026-bjp-releases-first-list-of-47-candidates-fields-rajeev-chandrasekhar-k-surendran/articleshow/129608012.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 16:39:37 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=11, tm_min=9, tm_sec=37, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI NEWS DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}}, {'title': 'Watch: Fire erupts again at Fujairah port in UAE, harbour suspends oil loadings', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Watch: Fire erupts again at Fujairah port in UAE, harbour suspends oil loadings'}, 'summary': "Fujairah port in the UAE experienced a drone attack, igniting a fire at a petroleum facility. While emergency teams quickly contained the blaze with no reported injuries, oil loadings were suspended. This marks a recent escalation in attacks on the vital oil hub, underscoring regional tensions and the port's critical role in global energy trade.", 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Fujairah port in the UAE experienced a drone attack, igniting a fire at a petroleum facility. While emergency teams quickly contained the blaze with no reported injuries, oil loadings were suspended. This marks a recent escalation in attacks on the vital oil hub, underscoring regional tensions and the port's critical role in global energy trade."}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubai-news-watch-fire-erupts-again-at-fujairah-port-in-uae-harbour-suspends-oil-loadings/articleshow/129604704.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '3113434', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129604822,imgsize-3113434.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubai-news-watch-fire-erupts-again-at-fujairah-port-in-uae-harbour-suspends-oil-loadings/articleshow/129604704.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubai-news-watch-fire-erupts-again-at-fujairah-port-in-uae-harbour-suspends-oil-loadings/articleshow/129604704.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 14:07:42 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=8, tm_min=37, tm_sec=42, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI WORLD DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI WORLD DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI WORLD DESK'}}, {'title': '‘Fees paid to Pak players aid those killing Indians’: Gavaskar slams Abrar signing', 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': '‘Fees paid to Pak players aid those killing Indians’: Gavaskar slams Abrar signing'}, 'summary': "Sunrisers Leeds' signing of Pakistani spinner Abrar Ahmed has ignited controversy in India, with Sunil Gavaskar urging Indian-owned franchises to avoid such deals. He argued that payments to Pakistani players indirectly fund their government, potentially harming India.  While the franchise cited cricketing reasons, the BCCI stated it cannot intervene in foreign league decisions.", 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Sunrisers Leeds' signing of Pakistani spinner Abrar Ahmed has ignited controversy in India, with Sunil Gavaskar urging Indian-owned franchises to avoid such deals. He argued that payments to Pakistani players indirectly fund their government, potentially harming India.  While the franchise cited cricketing reasons, the BCCI stated it cannot intervene in foreign league decisions."}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/cricket/news/fees-paid-to-pakistan-players-aid-those-killing-indians-sunil-gavaskar-slams-abrar-ahmed-signing-by-sunrisers-leeds/articleshow/129605747.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '72460', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129605754,imgsize-72460.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/cricket/news/fees-paid-to-pakistan-players-aid-those-killing-indians-sunil-gavaskar-slams-abrar-ahmed-signing-by-sunrisers-leeds/articleshow/129605747.cm