-fit-321m-former-minnesota-vikings-quarterback/articleshow/129574378.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '51984', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129574378,imgsize-51984.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/nfl/news/nfl-trade-rumors-jordan-loves-green-bay-packers-could-fit-321m-former-minnesota-vikings-quarterback/articleshow/129574378.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/nfl/news/nfl-trade-rumors-jordan-loves-green-bay-packers-could-fit-321m-former-minnesota-vikings-quarterback/articleshow/129574378.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Sat, 14 Mar 2026 20:46:00 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=14, tm_hour=15, tm_min=16, tm_sec=0, tm_wday=5, tm_yday=73, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'DR. ARATI KULKARNI SRIVASTAVA'}], 'author': 'DR. ARATI KULKARNI SRIVASTAVA', 'author_detail': {'name': 'DR. ARATI KULKARNI SRIVASTAVA'}}, {'title': "The 'files' of Bengaluru techies", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "The 'files' of Bengaluru techies"}, 'summary': "Bengaluru's tech boom hides a dark reality of distress. Cases of software engineers dying by suicide or facing accusations of violence highlight isolation, marital conflict, and immense pressure.  From dowry harassment to startup failures, these tragedies expose the human cost behind urban professional success, demanding urgent attention to mental well-being and support systems.", 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Bengaluru's tech boom hides a dark reality of distress. Cases of software engineers dying by suicide or facing accusations of violence highlight isolation, marital conflict, and immense pressure.  From dowry harassment to startup failures, these tragedies expose the human cost behind