e criticism, Federer remains one of tennis’ greatest champions and a billionaire through endorsements and investments.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/roger-federer-image-questioned-after-roland-garros-insider-claims-rafael-nadal-felt-more-authentic-and-less-money-focused/articleshow/129597979.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '2004911', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129597974,imgsize-2004911.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/roger-federer-image-questioned-after-roland-garros-insider-claims-rafael-nadal-felt-more-authentic-and-less-money-focused/articleshow/129597979.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/roger-federer-image-questioned-after-roland-garros-insider-claims-rafael-nadal-felt-more-authentic-and-less-money-focused/articleshow/129597979.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 05:35:00 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=0, tm_min=5, tm_sec=0, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'SEHJAL GUPTA'}], 'author': 'SEHJAL GUPTA', 'author_detail': {'name': 'SEHJAL GUPTA'}}, {'title': "Planning to buy property in India as NRI? Here's why it might not be a good idea", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "Planning to buy property in India as NRI? Here's why it might not be a good idea"}, 'summary': 'Non-resident Indians investing heavily in Indian real estate face challenges as properties may not yield expected financial returns or security. Experts warn of obsolescence in older flats, complications with family-gifted properties, and reduced value due to currency depreciation. Managing these illiquid assets from abroad also proves difficult.', 'summary_detail': {'type': 'text/html', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': 'Non-resident Indians investing heavily in Indian real estate face challenges as properties may not yield expected financial returns or security. Experts warn of obsolescence in older flats, complications with family-gifted properties, and reduced value due to currency depreciation. Managing these illiquid assets from abroad also proves difficult.'}, 'links': [{'rel': 'alternate', 'type': 'text/html', 'href': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/real-estate/news/planning-to-buy-property-in-india-as-nri-heres-why-it-might-not-be-a-good-idea/articleshow/129606013.cms'}, {'type': 'image/jpeg', 'length': '216313', 'href': 'https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-129607497,imgsize-216313.cms', 'rel': 'enclosure'}], 'link': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/real-estate/news/planning-to-buy-property-in-india-as-nri-heres-why-it-might-not-be-a-good-idea/articleshow/129606013.cms', 'id': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/real-estate/news/planning-to-buy-property-in-india-as-nri-heres-why-it-might-not-be-a-good-idea/articleshow/129606013.cms', 'guidislink': False, 'published': 'Mon, 16 Mar 2026 16:15:02 +0530', 'published_parsed': time.struct_time(tm_year=2026, tm_mon=3, tm_mday=16, tm_hour=10, tm_min=45, tm_sec=2, tm_wday=0, tm_yday=75, tm_isdst=0), 'authors': [{'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}], 'author': 'TOI NEWS DESK', 'author_detail': {'name': 'TOI NEWS DESK'}}, {'title': "'Targeted for being Hardeep Puri's daughter': Defamation plea in HC over Epstein posts", 'title_detail': {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeedstopstories.cms', 'value': "'Targeted for being Hardeep Puri's daughter': Defamation plea in HC over Epstein posts"}, 'summary': "Union Minister Hardeep Singh Puri's daughter has filed a plea in the Delhi High Court, seeking legal action against individuals and online platforms. She alleges defa